flow.mentorSays:
Let's understand what this Modal Dialog challenge asks for.

**Challenge Description:**
// Create a modal component:
// - "Open Modal" button
// - Modal with overlay (semi-transparent background)
// - Modal content (title, text, close button)
// - Close on clicking X button
// - Close on clicking overlay (outside modal)
// - Close on pressing ESC key
// - Prevent body scroll when open (bonus)

**What we need to build:**
This challenge tests your understanding of Portal, event handling.

**Time estimate:** 15 minutes
**Difficulty level:** Mid

This is a practical interview question that tests your understanding of core Angular concepts and your ability to implement them correctly.

